snippet.title: [HQ] Starcraft - First Trailer - 1996
snippet.description:
This video is often falsely dated to 1995, because it can be found on a Warcraft II disc. However the disc in question is the 1.22 rerelease and the video's timestamp is Jul 29, 1996. The full blizdemo from that CD is available here, along with other ones:
http://www.blizzardarchive.com/pub/index.php?id=blizdemo
